" {MPLTEXT 1 0 0 "" }}{PARA 232 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 201 22 "  for n f
rom 1 to N do" }{MPLTEXT 1 201 0 "" }}{PARA 232 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 
